text: Seven Vengeful Women (; ) is a 1966 Spanish Italian Austrian Liechtenstein western movie directed by Rudolf Zehetgruber and Sidney W. Pink. It stars Anne Baxter, Maria Perschy, Gustavo Rojo and Perla Cristal. == Other websites == * * * Category:1966 movies Category:1960s Western (genre) movies Category:Spanish Western (genre) movies Category:Italian Western (genre) movies Category:Austrian movies Category:Liechtenstein movies Category:Movies directed by Rudolf Zehetgruber Category:Movies directed by Sidney W.
